<para id="RM000001PR4005X" category="J" type-id="3024U" name-id="TD052-05" from="200601">
<dtccode/>
<dtcname>Horn Circuit</dtcname>
<subpara id="RM000001PR4005X_01" type-id="60" category="03" proc-id="RM0250U___00005EZ00001">
<name>DESCRIPTION</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<ptxt>When the theft deterrent system is switched from the armed state to the alarm sounding state, the main body ECU transmits a signal to cause the horn to sound at intervals of 0.4 seconds.</ptxt>
</content5>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM000001PR4005X_02" type-id="32" category="03" proc-id="RM0250U___00005F000001">
